attribute.description:
Toggles the ability to automatically clear the inner buffer storage when buffers are output.
0 = Don't: no autoclear; 

1 = Restart Counting: only restart the automatic counting of sample indices; 

2 = Clear Buffers: restart automatic counting and clear existing buffers;

Sets the collections mode: 

0 = Overwrite: new values at the same index of others overwrite the previous ones; 

1 = Overlap-Add: new values at the same index of others sums with the previous ones;
